snippet.title: Blocky Farm - Official New Platforms Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the new platform release trailer for Blocky Farm, a farm managing simulator developed by Forever Entertainment. Players will manage the farmlands, care for animals, and deliver the fruits of their labor to the town's citizens to establish happy customers. Blocky Farm is available now for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam and GoG).

#BlockyFarm #Gaming #IGN
